# Number

12

# Role

Naïve user of the data catalogue on a small screen

# Goal

A naïve visitor to the data catalogue on a small screen can click around through items in the menu ribbon and end up where they would expect

# Steps

| Step | Action | Expected result | Github bug/issue | Playwright test |
| ---- | ------ | --------------- |----------------- | --------------- |
| 1 | Navigate to [catalogue/](https://data-catalogue-acc.molgeniscloud.org/testCatalogue/catalogue/) | Landing page: European health research data and sample catalogue. The ribbon reads: 'MENU'`MOLGENIS` logo at the top and `HOME`, `ALL COLLECTIONS`, `ALL VARIABLES`, `ALL NETWORKS` below | | |
| 2 | Hover over the `MENU` button | It stays the same size| | |
